{% comment %}
  Returns & Exchanges Policy Page
{% endcomment %}

<div class="pt-32 pb-24 min-h-screen bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <h1 class="font-serif-display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-2 text-gray-900">{{ page.title }}</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %Y' }}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700">
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
        <p>We're confident you'll love your La Hime pieces. If you don't, we offer a 30-day return window for a full refund, no questions asked.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Return Eligibility</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Items must be unworn and unwashed</li>
          <li>Original tags must be attached</li>
          <li>Items must be in original condition</li>
          <li>Return is initiated within 30 days of purchase</li>
          <li>Applies to full-price items (sale items may have different terms)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">How to Return</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-2 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Log into your account and go to Order History</li>
          <li>Select the order containing the item to return</li>
          <li>Click "Return Item" and follow the prompts</li>
          <li>Print your prepaid shipping label</li>
          <li>Pack your item securely and drop off at any carrier location</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">All returns include prepaid shippingâ€”no surprises!</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Exchanges</h2>
        <p>Need a different size or color? We offer free exchanges within 30 days of purchase. Go to your order and select "Exchange Item" to get started.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Refunds</h2>
        <p>Once we receive and inspect your return, refunds are processed within 5-7 business days. The refund will be credited to your original payment method.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Items Not Eligible for Return</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Worn or washed items</li>
          <li>Items without original tags</li>
          <li>Items showing signs of wear or alteration</li>
          <li>Final sale or clearance items (marked at checkout)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="bg-pink-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-pink-200 mt-12">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Questions about returns?</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@lahime.com" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">contact@lahime.com</a> for assistance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .font-serif-display { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
</style>
